[2.0750, "o", "-"]
[2.1000, "o", "h"]
[2.1250, "o", "e"]
[2.1500, "o", "l"]
[2.1750, "o", "p"]
[2.2000, "o", "\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.2800, "o", "Age-based secrets management with transport-agnostic sharing\r\n\r\nUsage: himitsu [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  init       Initialize himitsu in the current project (or globally)\r\n  set        Set a secret value\r\n  get        Get a secret value\r\n  ls         List environments or secrets\r\n  encrypt    Re-encrypt secrets for current recipients\r\n  decrypt    Decrypt secrets (not supported - secrets are never stored in plaintext)\r\n  sync       Sync secrets with a remote store\r\n  search     Search secrets across all known projects\r\n  recipient  Manage recipients\r\n  group      Manage recipient groups\r\n  remote     Manage remote sync targets\r\n  schema     Generate and manage JSON schemas\r\n  codegen    Generate typed config code from secrets\r\n  git        Run git commands inside the himitsu directory (~/.himitsu)\r\n  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n  -s, --store <STORE>  Override the store path (default: $GIT_ROOT/.himitsu/ or ~/.himitsu/)\r\n  -v, --verbose...     Increase log verbosity (-v for debug, -vv for trace)\r\n  -h, --help           Print help\r\n  -V, --version        Print version\r\n"]
[2.3300, "o", "\r\n"]
[3.0300, "o", "\r\n"]
